column3: Viking Motorcycles UnVeiling of their Custom

Viking Motorcycle the Valkyrie Riders Cruiser Club's largest vendor unveiling of their Custom build specifically for the Biker Build-off Program Metric-Revolution. Viking began customizing Valkyries and if Honda had the sense to still be making Hondas thats what Viking would be building. They still support the Valkyrie in parts and innovations and you can find them at VikingMotorcycle.com
